    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty! It is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I've babied it from day one, and it really shows. Not a scratch in sight, and the interior is still smelling fresh. It drives like an absolute dream and has been kept tucked away in a garage. I\u2019m honestly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love instantly. Come swing by and take it for a spin\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
