      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a peerless example of the legendary S54 platform. It features the high-revving 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing, providing instantaneous throttle response and a linear power band to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, mechanical engagement, paired with a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. This specimen is mechanically sorted with documented rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural integrity of the chassis. The suspension remains taut with original damping characteristics, and the exterior retains its factory-applied finish with no signs of oxidation or clear coat failure. A turn-key collector-grade vehicle for the serious driving enthusiast.",
      "price": 46500.0,
